    div.Accordion-question What does “diversity” mean to the CTDI Slack group?
    div.Accordion-answer
      p This is an intentionally anti-sexist, anti-racist, anti-homophobic, anti-transphobic, anti-ablest, anti-discrimination, and anti-harassment space. We value inclusion through and through!

